### PRODUCT ROUTES ###

### Get all product recommendations for a user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=MzCTihlddchzDsiVoAjcHbxGaRt1

### Get recommendations with limit
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=MzCTihlddchzDsiVoAjcHbxGaRt1&limit=5

### Get Shampoo recommendations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=MzCTihlddchzDsiVoAjcHbxGaRt1&category=Shampoos&limit=5

### Get Conditioner recommendations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=MzCTihlddchzDsiVoAjcHbxGaRt1&category=Conditioners&limit=5

### Get Leave-in Conditioner recommendations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=MzCTihlddchzDsiVoAjcHbxGaRt1&category=Leave-in Conditioners&limit=3

### Get Hair Oils recommendations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=MzCTihlddchzDsiVoAjcHbxGaRt1&category=Hair Oils&limit=5

### Get Hair Masks recommendations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=MzCTihlddchzDsiVoAjcHbxGaRt1&category=Hair Masks&limit=3

### Test error: Missing userId
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations

### Test error: Invalid userId
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productRecommendations?userId=invalid-user-id